---
title: Chermoula Aubergine with Bulgur Wheat and Salsa
description: Fresh, fast and packed with healthy ingredients, this delicious dish is a great recipe for a light mid-week dinner. We’ve marinated red peppers and aubergine in a delicious mix of chermoula, honey and olive oil, before roasting until soft and golden. Served with nutty bulgur wheat, creamy feta and a chunky cucumber salsa, and finished off with a good squeeze of fresh lemon juice.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/chermoula-aubergine-257eaddb-45025a78.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/chermoula-aubergine-5d286c06bd9e79000f3f9036-3acf5848.pdf
servings: 2
source: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipes/chermoula-aubergine-5d286c06bd9e79000f3f9036
time required: 40 minutes
cuisine: Fusion
course: main course
author: HelloFresh
